flowchart TD
  Start([Enter Maventor]) --> Landing[Open Mentor Dashboard]
  Landing --> HasProfile{Profile complete?}
  HasProfile -- No --> Profile[Complete Mentor Profile]
  Profile --> SaveProfile[Save Expertise and Availability]
  SaveProfile --> WaitPairing[Wait for Officer Assignment]
  HasProfile -- Yes --> PairCheck{Pairing assigned?}
  WaitPairing --> PairCheck

  PairCheck -- No --> PairingPending[View Pending Status]
  PairingPending --> RefreshStatus[Refresh or return later]
  RefreshStatus --> PairCheck

  PairCheck -- Yes --> ActivePair[Open Active Pairing]
  ActivePair --> Chat[Respond in Direct Messages]
  ActivePair --> Goals[Review Mentee Goals]
  ActivePair --> CheckIn[Submit Mentor Feedback]
  CheckIn --> CompatView[Review Compatibility Indicator]
  Goals --> ActionPlan[Set Next Action Items]
  Chat --> ActionPlan
  CompatView --> ActionPlan
  ActionPlan --> End([Continue Mentorship Cycle])
